AUSTRALIA: RTRS-Australis in US$105 mln finance deal.RTRS-Australis in US$105 mln finance deal.Australis Media Ltd said on Tuesday a consortium involving Kerry Packer's Publishing and Broadcasting Ltd and Lenfest Communications Inc would provide the company with US$105 million of equity finance.Australis also said it had concluded a joint venture agreement to share DTH satellite infractructure with fellow pay television operator Optus Vision.